{
  "video_id": "k5tCYg9s0HU",
  "title": "A letter to all who have lost in this era | Anand Giridharadas",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12870.0,
      "end_time": 17189.0,
      "text": "June 29, 2016."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 19150.0,
      "end_time": 21200.0,
      "text": "My dear fellow citizen:"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 22775.0,
      "end_time": 25760.0,
      "text": "I write to you today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 26393.0,
      "end_time": 29949.0,
      "text": "to you who have lost in this era."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 31708.0,
      "end_time": 35551.0,
      "text": "At this moment in our common life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 35950.0,
      "end_time": 37820.0,
      "text": "when the world is full of breaking"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 38425.0,
      "end_time": 39695.0,
      "text": "and spite"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 40239.0,
      "end_time": 41504.0,
      "text": "and fear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 43385.0,
      "end_time": 45129.0,
      "text": "I address this letter"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 45863.0,
      "end_time": 47644.0,
      "text": "simply to you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 48494.0,
      "end_time": 50620.0,
      "text": "even though we both know"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 50860.0,
      "end_time": 54228.0,
      "text": "there are many of you behind this \"you,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 55306.0,
      "end_time": 59240.0,
      "text": "and many of me behind this \"I.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 62525.0,
      "end_time": 65810.0,
      "text": "I write to you because at present,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 66478.0,
      "end_time": 70798.0,
      "text": "this quaking world we share scares me."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 72819.0,
      "end_time": 74810.0,
      "text": "I gather it scares you, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 76618.0,
      "end_time": 79646.0,
      "text": "Some of what we fear, I suspect,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 79671.0,
      "end_time": 81260.0,
      "text": "we fear in common."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 82169.0,
      "end_time": 86533.0,
      "text": "But much of what we fear seems to be each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 88736.0,
      "end_time": 91656.0,
      "text": "You fear the world I want to live in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 92529.0,
      "end_time": 96417.0,
      "text": "and I fear your visions in turn."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 97673.0,
      "end_time": 102446.0,
      "text": "Do you know that feeling you get when you know it&#39;s going to storm"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 102470.0,
      "end_time": 104170.0,
      "text": "before it storms?"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 106100.0,
      "end_time": 108469.0,
      "text": "Do you also feel that now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 109276.0,
      "end_time": 110515.0,
      "text": "fellow citizen?"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 112435.0,
      "end_time": 115157.0,
      "text": "That malaise and worry"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 116181.0,
      "end_time": 117770.0,
      "text": "that some who know"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 119517.0,
      "end_time": 122183.0,
      "text": "feel reminds them of the 1930s?"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 123878.0,
      "end_time": 125747.0,
      "text": "Perhaps you don&#39;t,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 126493.0,
      "end_time": 128400.0,
      "text": "because our fears of each other"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 128424.0,
      "end_time": 129943.0,
      "text": "are not in sync."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 131325.0,
      "end_time": 134801.0,
      "text": "In this round, I sense that your fears of me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 135655.0,
      "end_time": 139700.0,
      "text": "of the world that I have insisted is right for us both,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 140856.0,
      "end_time": 142686.0,
      "text": "has gathered over a generation."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 144170.0,
      "end_time": 148136.0,
      "text": "It took time for your fears to trigger my fears,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 148868.0,
      "end_time": 151626.0,
      "text": "not least because at first,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 151666.0,
      "end_time": 154355.0,
      "text": "I never thought I needed to fear you."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 156882.0,
      "end_time": 158219.0,
      "text": "I heard you"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 159737.0,
      "end_time": 161700.0,
      "text": "but did not listen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 161731.0,
      "end_time": 166728.0,
      "text": "all these years when you said that this amazing new world"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 168204.0,
      "end_time": 169754.0,
      "text": "wasn&#39;t amazing for you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 170879.0,
      "end_time": 172483.0,
      "text": "for many of you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 172507.0,
      "end_time": 175300.0,
      "text": "across the industrialized world;"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 175918.0,
      "end_time": 178739.0,
      "text": "that the open, liquid world I relished,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 178763.0,
      "end_time": 183660.0,
      "text": "of people and goods and technologies flowing freely,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 183900.0,
      "end_time": 185530.0,
      "text": "going where they pleased, globally,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 187190.0,
      "end_time": 191279.0,
      "text": "was not, for you, an emancipation."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 193453.0,
      "end_time": 195894.0,
      "text": "I have walked through your towns"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 197442.0,
      "end_time": 201182.0,
      "text": "and, while looking, failed to see."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 202799.0,
      "end_time": 206730.0,
      "text": "I did notice in Stephenville, Texas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 207791.0,
      "end_time": 210970.0,
      "text": "that the town square was dominated"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 210122.0,
      "end_time": 213365.0,
      "text": "by one lawyer&#39;s office after another,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 214394.0,
      "end_time": 217395.0,
      "text": "because of all the people rotating in and out of the prison."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 218224.0,
      "end_time": 222302.0,
      "text": "I did notice the barren shops in Wagner, South Dakota,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 223925.0,
      "end_time": 227403.0,
      "text": "and the VFW gathering hall"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 228314.0,
      "end_time": 230106.0,
      "text": "that stood in mockery"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 230934.0,
      "end_time": 233725.0,
      "text": "of a community&#39;s dream to endure."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 235352.0,
      "end_time": 236566.0,
      "text": "I did notice"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 237323.0,
      "end_time": 240748.0,
      "text": "at the Lancaster, Pennsylvania Wal-Mart,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 241445.0,
      "end_time": 245804.0,
      "text": "that far too many people in their 20s and 30s"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 245828.0,
      "end_time": 248335.0,
      "text": "looked a decade or two from death,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 249295.0,
      "end_time": 251641.0,
      "text": "with patchy, flared-up skin"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 251665.0,
      "end_time": 254141.0,
      "text": "and thinning, stringy hair"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 254165.0,
      "end_time": 255816.0,
      "text": "and browning, ground-down teeth"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 255841.0,
      "end_time": 259102.0,
      "text": "and a lostness in their eyes."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 260160.00000000003,
      "end_time": 264770.0,
      "text": "I did notice that the young people I encountered in Paris,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 264794.0,
      "end_time": 266745.0,
      "text": "in Florence, in Barcelona,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 266769.0,
      "end_time": 270279.0,
      "text": "had degrees but no place to take them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 271712.0,
      "end_time": 274676.0,
      "text": "living on internships well into their 30s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 275693.0,
      "end_time": 278589.0,
      "text": "their lives prevented from launching,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 279868.0,
      "end_time": 282614.0,
      "text": "because of an economy that creates wealth --"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 283409.0,
      "end_time": 284748.0,
      "text": "just not jobs."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 285836.0,
      "end_time": 292138.0,
      "text": "I did notice the news about those parts of London becoming ghost quarters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 293250.0,
      "end_time": 298693.0,
      "text": "where the global super-rich turn fishy money into empty apartments"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 299962.0,
      "end_time": 304630.0,
      "text": "and price lifelong residents of a city, young couples starting out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 304880.0,
      "end_time": 305803.0,
      "text": "out of their own home."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 308332.0,
      "end_time": 311253.0,
      "text": "And I heard that the fabric of your life"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 311277.0,
      "end_time": 312522.0,
      "text": "was tearing."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 313574.0,
      "end_time": 315978.0,
      "text": "You used to be able to count on work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 316840.0,
      "end_time": 318169.0,
      "text": "and now you couldn&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 318977.0,
      "end_time": 321816.0,
      "text": "You used to be able to nourish your children,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 323790.0,
      "end_time": 325420.0,
      "text": "and guarantee that they would climb"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 326520.0,
      "end_time": 329978.0,
      "text": "a little bit further in life than you had,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 330200.0,
      "end_time": 331295.0,
      "text": "and now you couldn&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 332374.0,
      "end_time": 337959.0,
      "text": "You used to be made to feel dignity in your work, and now you didn&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 339795.0,
      "end_time": 343191.0,
      "text": "It used to be normal for people like you to own a home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 344470.0,
      "end_time": 345849.0,
      "text": "and now it wasn&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 347286.0,
      "end_time": 349466.0,
      "text": "I cannot say"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 350426.0,
      "end_time": 352217.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t know these things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 353701.0,
      "end_time": 355918.0,
      "text": "but I was distracted"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 357569.0,
      "end_time": 360987.0,
      "text": "creating a future in which we could live on Mars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 363910.0,
      "end_time": 366451.0,
      "text": "even as you struggled down here on Earth."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 368155.0,
      "end_time": 369614.0,
      "text": "I was distracted"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 370455.0,
      "end_time": 372289.0,
      "text": "innovating immortality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 374519.0,
      "end_time": 379312.0,
      "text": "even as many of you began to live shorter lives than your parents had."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 381301.0,
      "end_time": 384360.0,
      "text": "I heard all of these things, but I didn&#39;t listen."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 385528.0,
      "end_time": 386727.0,
      "text": "I looked"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 387566.0,
      "end_time": 389137.0,
      "text": "but didn&#39;t see."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 389161.0,
      "end_time": 392286.0,
      "text": "I read, didn&#39;t understand."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 393370.0,
      "end_time": 394576.0,
      "text": "I paid attention"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 395389.0,
      "end_time": 399261.0,
      "text": "only when you began to vote and shout,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 400428.0,
      "end_time": 403492.0,
      "text": "and when your voting and shouting, when the substance of it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 403516.0,
      "end_time": 405999.0,
      "text": "began to threaten me."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 408235.0,
      "end_time": 413228.0,
      "text": "I listened only when you moved toward shattering continental unions"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 413252.0,
      "end_time": 415513.0,
      "text": "and electing vulgar demagogues."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 416704.0,
      "end_time": 420608.0,
      "text": "Only then did your pain become of interest"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 421343.0,
      "end_time": 422508.0,
      "text": "to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 424317.0,
      "end_time": 426271.0,
      "text": "I know that feeling hurt"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 426295.0,
      "end_time": 429588.0,
      "text": "is often prologue to dealing hurt."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 431664.0,
      "end_time": 433440.0,
      "text": "I wonder now"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 434408.0,
      "end_time": 436686.0,
      "text": "if you would be less eager to deal it"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 437438.0,
      "end_time": 439378.0,
      "text": "if I had stood with you"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 439402.0,
      "end_time": 441686.0,
      "text": "when you merely felt it."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 443313.0,
      "end_time": 444590.0,
      "text": "I ask myself"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 445355.0,
      "end_time": 447448.0,
      "text": "why I didn&#39;t stand with you then."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 448874.0,
      "end_time": 452251.0,
      "text": "One reason is that I became entranced"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 452275.0,
      "end_time": 454364.0,
      "text": "by the gurus of change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 455187.0,
      "end_time": 459522.0,
      "text": "became a worshiper of the religion of the new for novelty&#39;s sake,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 459546.0,
      "end_time": 461699.0,
      "text": "and of globalization and open borders"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 461723.0,
      "end_time": 464660.0,
      "text": "and kaleidoscopic diversity."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 466928.0,
      "end_time": 470836.0,
      "text": "Once change became my totalizing faith,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 472415.0,
      "end_time": 473817.0,
      "text": "I could be blind."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 475143.0,
      "end_time": 478676.0,
      "text": "I could fail to see change&#39;s consequences."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 479866.0,
      "end_time": 481803.0,
      "text": "I could overlook the importance"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 481827.0,
      "end_time": 484929.0,
      "text": "of roots, traditions, rituals, stability --"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 484953.0,
      "end_time": 486296.0,
      "text": "and belonging."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 487501.0,
      "end_time": 490816.0,
      "text": "And the more fundamentalist I became"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 490840.0,
      "end_time": 494582.0,
      "text": "in my worship of change and openness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 496900.0,
      "end_time": 499320.0,
      "text": "the more I drove you towards the other polarity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 500740.0,
      "end_time": 501234.0,
      "text": "to cling,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 501632.0,
      "end_time": 502789.0,
      "text": "to freeze,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 503277.0,
      "end_time": 504448.0,
      "text": "to close,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 505100.0,
      "end_time": 506259.0,
      "text": "to belong."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 508138.0,
      "end_time": 510854.0,
      "text": "I now see as I didn&#39;t before"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 510878.0,
      "end_time": 514818.0,
      "text": "that not having the right skin or right organ"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 514842.0,
      "end_time": 518765.0,
      "text": "is not the only varietal of disadvantage."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 519722.0,
      "end_time": 523312.0,
      "text": "There is a subtler, quieter disadvantage"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 523336.0,
      "end_time": 526651.0,
      "text": "in having those privileged traits"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 526675.0,
      "end_time": 531580.0,
      "text": "and yet feeling history to be moving away from you;"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 531820.0,
      "end_time": 534475.0,
      "text": "that while the past was hospitable to people like you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 534499.0,
      "end_time": 536897.0,
      "text": "the future will be more hospitable"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 536921.0,
      "end_time": 538314.0,
      "text": "to others;"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 538338.0,
      "end_time": 540790.0,
      "text": "that the world is growing less familiar,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 540815.0,
      "end_time": 543681.0,
      "text": "less yours day by day."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 545865.0,
      "end_time": 551547.0,
      "text": "I will not concede for a moment that old privileges should not dwindle."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 552550.0,
      "end_time": 554800.0,
      "text": "They cannot dwindle fast enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 555785.0,
      "end_time": 559285.0,
      "text": "It is for you to learn to live in a new century in which"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 559310.0,
      "end_time": 564133.0,
      "text": "there are no bonuses for showing up with the right skin and right organs."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 565277.0,
      "end_time": 567704.0,
      "text": "If and when your anger turns to hate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 567729.0,
      "end_time": 571959.0,
      "text": "please know that there is no space for that in our shared home."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 573642.0,
      "end_time": 576990.0,
      "text": "But I will admit, fellow citizen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 578140.0,
      "end_time": 583679.0,
      "text": "that I have discounted the burden of coping with the loss of status."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 584163.0,
      "end_time": 585932.0,
      "text": "I have forgotten"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 585957.0,
      "end_time": 590702.0,
      "text": "that what is socially necessary can also be personally gruelling."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 592919.0,
      "end_time": 594424.0,
      "text": "A similar thing happened"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 595217.0,
      "end_time": 598841.0,
      "text": "with the economy that you and I share."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 600191.0,
      "end_time": 602623.0,
      "text": "Just as I cannot and don&#39;t wish"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 602647.0,
      "end_time": 606274.0,
      "text": "to turn back to the clock on equality and diversity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 606298.0,
      "end_time": 608627.0,
      "text": "and yet must understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 608651.0,
      "end_time": 611416.0,
      "text": "the sense of loss they can inspire,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 613270.0,
      "end_time": 617185.0,
      "text": "so, too, I refuse and could not if I wished"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 617970.0,
      "end_time": 622111.0,
      "text": "turn back the clock on an ever more closely knit, interdependent world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 622135.0,
      "end_time": 625525.0,
      "text": "and on inventions that won&#39;t stop being invented."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 626520.0,
      "end_time": 631754.0,
      "text": "And yet I must understand your experience of these things."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 633320.0,
      "end_time": 636451.0,
      "text": "You have for years been telling me that your experience of these things"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 636475.0,
      "end_time": 639617.0,
      "text": "is not as good as my theories forecast."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 640528.0,
      "end_time": 644386.0,
      "text": "Yet before you could finish a complaining sentence"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 646116.0,
      "end_time": 651604.0,
      "text": "about the difficulty of living with erratic hours, volatile pay,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 651628.0,
      "end_time": 653254.0,
      "text": "vanishing opportunities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 653278.0,
      "end_time": 657536.0,
      "text": "about the pain of dropping your children off at 24-hour day care"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 657560.0,
      "end_time": 659323.0,
      "text": "to make your 3am shift,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 660319.0,
      "end_time": 664232.0,
      "text": "I shot back at you -- before you could finish your sentence --"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 664256.0,
      "end_time": 665598.0,
      "text": "my dogma,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 665622.0,
      "end_time": 670510.0,
      "text": "about how what you are actually experiencing was flexibility"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 670794.0,
      "end_time": 672790.0,
      "text": "and freedom."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 674591.0,
      "end_time": 679162.0,
      "text": "Language is one of the only things that we truly share,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 680549.0,
      "end_time": 684280.0,
      "text": "and I sometimes used this joint inheritance"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 684520.0,
      "end_time": 685263.0,
      "text": "to obfuscate"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 685821.0,
      "end_time": 687250.0,
      "text": "and deflect"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 687479.0,
      "end_time": 688995.0,
      "text": "and justify myself;"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 689933.0,
      "end_time": 691813.0,
      "text": "to re-brand what was good for me"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 691837.0,
      "end_time": 694629.0,
      "text": "as something appearing good for us both,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 695324.0,
      "end_time": 699310.0,
      "text": "when I threw around terms like \"the sharing economy,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 700135.0,
      "end_time": 701310.0,
      "text": "and \"disruption\""
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 701845.0,
      "end_time": 703690.0,
      "text": "and \"global resourcing.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 705224.0,
      "end_time": 707595.0,
      "text": "I see now that what I was really doing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 708229.0,
      "end_time": 709475.0,
      "text": "at times,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 709894.0,
      "end_time": 712998.0,
      "text": "was buying your pain on the cheap,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 713892.0,
      "end_time": 715104.0,
      "text": "sprucing it up"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 715772.0,
      "end_time": 717744.0,
      "text": "and trying to sell it back to you"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 718244.0,
      "end_time": 719450.0,
      "text": "as freedom."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 721712.0,
      "end_time": 724971.0,
      "text": "I have wanted to believe and wanted you to believe"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 727683.0,
      "end_time": 729792.0,
      "text": "that the system that has been good to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 729816.0,
      "end_time": 732489.0,
      "text": "that has made my life ever more seamless,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 733229.0,
      "end_time": 736124.0,
      "text": "is also the best system for you."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 737544.0,
      "end_time": 739805.0,
      "text": "I have condescended to you"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 739829.0,
      "end_time": 743724.0,
      "text": "with the idea that you are voting against your economic interests --"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 744207.0,
      "end_time": 745995.0,
      "text": "voting against your interests,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 747621.0,
      "end_time": 750843.0,
      "text": "as if I know your interests."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 752296.0,
      "end_time": 756613.0,
      "text": "That is just my dogmatic economism talking."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 757723.0,
      "end_time": 759500.0,
      "text": "I have a weakness"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 759524.0,
      "end_time": 764909.0,
      "text": "for treating people&#39;s economic interests as their only interest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 764933.0,
      "end_time": 768457.0,
      "text": "ignoring things like belonging and pride"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 768481.0,
      "end_time": 772255.0,
      "text": "and the desire to send a message to those who ignore you."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 772688.0,
      "end_time": 775419.0,
      "text": "So here we are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 776243.0,
      "end_time": 780869.0,
      "text": "in a scary but not inexplicable moment"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 781507.0,
      "end_time": 783829.0,
      "text": "of demagoguery, fracture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 784481.0,
      "end_time": 788367.0,
      "text": "xenophobia, resentment and fear."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 789628.0,
      "end_time": 793658.0,
      "text": "And I worry for us both if we continue down this road,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 794358.0,
      "end_time": 795753.0,
      "text": "me not listening,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 796305.0,
      "end_time": 798156.0,
      "text": "you feeling unheard,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 798180.0,
      "end_time": 800728.0,
      "text": "you shouting to get me to listen."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 802779.0,
      "end_time": 806230.0,
      "text": "I worry when each of us is seduced by visions of the future"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 806254.0,
      "end_time": 808914.0,
      "text": "that have no place for the other."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 809731.0,
      "end_time": 811819.0,
      "text": "If this goes on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 813655.0,
      "end_time": 815300.0,
      "text": "if this goes on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 816530.0,
      "end_time": 817532.0,
      "text": "there may be blood."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 819290.0,
      "end_time": 821974.0,
      "text": "There are already hints of this blood"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 822915.0,
      "end_time": 824255.0,
      "text": "in newspapers every day."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 824967.0,
      "end_time": 827552.0,
      "text": "There may be roundups, raids,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 827586.0,
      "end_time": 830661.0,
      "text": "deportations, camps, secessions."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 831494.0,
      "end_time": 834415.0,
      "text": "And no, I do not think that I exaggerate."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 836236.0,
      "end_time": 838157.0,
      "text": "There may be even talk of war"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 838181.0,
      "end_time": 841731.0,
      "text": "in places that were certain they were done with it."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 843483.0,
      "end_time": 847228.0,
      "text": "There is always the hope of redemption."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 847764.0,
      "end_time": 851420.0,
      "text": "But it will not be a cheap, shallow redemption"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 851660.0,
      "end_time": 854737.0,
      "text": "that comes through blather about us all being in it together."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 855312.0,
      "end_time": 857168.0,
      "text": "This will take more."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 858396.0,
      "end_time": 863588.0,
      "text": "It will take accepting that we both made choices to be here."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 865863.0,
      "end_time": 868966.0,
      "text": "We create our \"others.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 869975.0,
      "end_time": 873655.0,
      "text": "As parents, as neighbors, as citizens,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 874503.0,
      "end_time": 878834.0,
      "text": "we witness and sometimes ignore each other"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 878858.0,
      "end_time": 880980.0,
      "text": "into being."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 881268.0,
      "end_time": 884318.0,
      "text": "You were not born vengeful."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 885339.0,
      "end_time": 887346.0,
      "text": "I have some role"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 887370.0,
      "end_time": 890871.0,
      "text": "in whatever thirst you now feel for revenge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 891685.0,
      "end_time": 893598.0,
      "text": "and that thirst now tempts me"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 893622.0,
      "end_time": 896140.0,
      "text": "to plot ever more elaborate escapes"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 896164.0,
      "end_time": 898830.0,
      "text": "from our common life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 898107.0,
      "end_time": 899976.0,
      "text": "from the schools and neighborhoods"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 900000.0,
      "end_time": 901931.0,
      "text": "and airports and amusement parks"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 901955.0,
      "end_time": 903596.0,
      "text": "that we used to share."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 905659.0,
      "end_time": 908647.0,
      "text": "We face, then,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 908671.0,
      "end_time": 912445.0,
      "text": "a problem not of these large, impersonal forces."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 914366.0,
      "end_time": 918518.0,
      "text": "We face a problem of your and my relations."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 919815.0,
      "end_time": 922953.0,
      "text": "We chose ways of relating to each other"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 924345.0,
      "end_time": 925496.0,
      "text": "that got us here."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 925896.0,
      "end_time": 928645.0,
      "text": "We can choose ways of relating"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 928669.0,
      "end_time": 930275.0,
      "text": "that get us out."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 931361.0,
      "end_time": 934630.0,
      "text": "But there are things we might have to let go of,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 935418.0,
      "end_time": 936599.0,
      "text": "fellow citizen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 937674.0,
      "end_time": 943280.0,
      "text": "starting with our own cherished versions of reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 945350.0,
      "end_time": 948904.0,
      "text": "Imagine if you let go of fantasies"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 948928.0,
      "end_time": 952786.0,
      "text": "of a society purged of these or those people."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 953561.0,
      "end_time": 957214.0,
      "text": "Imagine if I let go of my habit"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 957755.0,
      "end_time": 960825.0,
      "text": "of saving the world behind your back,"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 961833.0,
      "end_time": 963230.0,
      "text": "of deliberating on the future"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 963254.0,
      "end_time": 964729.0,
      "text": "of your work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 965260.0,
      "end_time": 966506.0,
      "text": "your food,"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 966530.0,
      "end_time": 968000.0,
      "text": "your schools,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 968240.0,
      "end_time": 971340.0,
      "text": "in places where you couldn&#39;t get past security."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 972386.0,
      "end_time": 976732.0,
      "text": "We can do this only if we first accept"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 977347.0,
      "end_time": 979990.0,
      "text": "that we have neglected each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 981971.0,
      "end_time": 985185.0,
      "text": "If there is hope to summon"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 985930.0,
      "end_time": 987280.0,
      "text": "in this ominous hour,"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 988202.0,
      "end_time": 989393.0,
      "text": "it is this."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 990870.0,
      "end_time": 992572.0,
      "text": "We have, for too long,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 993547.0,
      "end_time": 996916.0,
      "text": "chased various shimmering dreams"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 997818.0,
      "end_time": 1003682.0,
      "text": "at the cost of attention to the foundational dream of each other,"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 1005100.0,
      "end_time": 1007668.0,
      "text": "the dream of tending to each other,"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 1007690.0,
      "end_time": 1010553.0,
      "text": "of unleashing each other&#39;s wonders,"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 1010580.0,
      "end_time": 1013125.0,
      "text": "of moving through history together."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 1014460.0,
      "end_time": 1018315.0,
      "text": "We could dare to commit to the dream of each other"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 1019900.0,
      "end_time": 1023716.0,
      "text": "as the thing that matters before every neon thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 1024480.0,
      "end_time": 1025962.0,
      "text": "Let us dare."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 1026470.0,
      "end_time": 1027630.0,
      "text": "Sincerely yours,"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 1028670.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1029242.0000000001,
      "text": "a fellow citizen."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
